title: Nicola Sturgeon quits: Scottish leader departure follows criticism of transgender agenda
description: Scottish First Minister Nicola Sturgeon is resigning from her role as the nation's leader in the wake of controversy and criticism over her support of transgender policies and gender identification reforms.

title: Nicola Sturgeon to resign as Scottish first minister
description: Nicola Sturgeon is reportedly set to resign as Scotland's first minister after more than eight years in the position.
